# Rust build artifacts
target/

# Knowledge scans: ignore all local snapshots (debug, ad-hoc tests)
# but KEEP structural baselines (*-baseline.json) generated via
# `meta save-structure` — those are version-safe regression references.
knowledge/scans/*
!knowledge/scans/*-baseline.json

